她在2006年与《[[70年代秀|70年代秀]]》中的[[托弗·格雷斯|托弗·格雷斯]]约会。<ref name="people">{{cite web | title=People.com | work=Ivanka Trump & Topher Grace Cozy Up | url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,1552878,00.html | accessdate=October 12, 2007 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824101858/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,1552878,00.html | archivedate=2007年8月24日 }}</ref>2009年7月，在与[[拉比|拉比]]埃利·温斯托克一起读书后，伊凡卡[[皈依犹太教|皈依犹太教]]<ref name=haaretz>{{Cite news|url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1032908.html|title=Report: Tycoon Donald Trump's daughter converting to Judaism|work=Haaretz|date=October 30, 2008|accessdate=2014-02-11|archive-date=2010-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419122149/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1032908.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Messer, Lesley. [http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20291939,00.html Ivanka Trump Converts to Judaism for Fiancé] {{Wayback|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20291939,00.html |date=20100420062522 }}, ''People magazine'', July 17, 2009. Accessed February 19, 2010.</ref>取教名Yael。<ref>''The View'', October 26, 2009</ref> 在2015年伊凡卡說：「對我來說這是一個偉大的生活決定。我真的發現，猶太教，它創建了一個驚人的家庭連接的藍圖。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vogue.com/11739787/ivanka-trump-collection-the-apprentice-family/|title=^ Ivanka Trump Knows What It Means to Be a Modern Millennial|date=February 25, 2015|work=Vogue.com|accessdate=2017-01-24|archive-date=2015-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150506192313/http://www.vogue.com/11739787/ivanka-trump-collection-the-apprentice-family|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年10月25日，伊凡卡与商人[[贾瑞德·库什纳|贾瑞德·库什纳]][[结婚|结婚]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20315305,00.html|title=^ Ivanka Trump Marries Jared Kusher in Lavish Ceremony|date=October 25, 2009|work=People.com|accessdate=February 21, 2011|archive-date=2012-08-11|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69ptuetLS?url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20315305,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[贾里德·库什纳|贾里德·库什纳]]的父亲查尔斯·库斯纳拥有库什纳地产集团，贾瑞德持有股份所有权。贾里德也是《纽约观察家》的老板。<ref>[[United_Press_International|United Press International]], [http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/04/nyregion/04wedding.html?_r=1/ Wedding Gifts for the Couple Who Have Everything] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/04/nyregion/04wedding.html?_r=1%2F |date=20200926012836 }} ''New York Times''</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://lexib.net/2009/10/ivanka-trump-jared-kushner-wed|title=Ivanka Trump, Jared Kushner Wed|author=LexiB|publisher="LexiB.net"|accessdate=2009-10-26|date=2009-10-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091104054242/http://lexib.net/2009/10/ivanka-trump-jared-kushner-wed/|archivedate=2009-11-04|df=}}</ref>2011年，伊凡卡的第一個女儿出生。<ref>[http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/ivanka-trump-and-jared-kushner-welcome-baby-girl/story-e6frf7jx-1226096593010 "Ivanka Trump and Jared Kushner welcome baby girl"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/news/breaking-news/ivanka-trump-and-jared-kushner-welcome-baby-girl/story-e6frf7jx-1226096593010 |date=20140906210736 }}. ''Herald Sun''. July 17, 2011. Retrieved July 17, 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/celebrities/ivanka-trump-tweets-birth-announcement-of-1st-child-a-daughter-born-in-nyc/2011/07/17/gIQAPW7VKI_story.html "Ivanka Trump tweets birth announcement of 1st child, a daughter born in NYC"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/celebrities/ivanka-trump-tweets-birth-announcement-of-1st-child-a-daughter-born-in-nyc/2011/07/17/gIQAPW7VKI_story.html |date=20160310125207 }}. ''Washington Post''. July 17, 2011. Retrieved July 17, 2011.</ref>2013年4月，伊凡卡宣布她怀了第二个孩子，同年生下長子。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mobile.twitter.com/IvankaTrump/status/322358423591190528|title=Jared and I are excited that Arabella will become a big sister this fall. Thanks for all your good wishes! xo Ivanka|publisher=Twitter|last=Trump|first=Ivanka|date=April 11, 2013|accessdate=May 21, 2013|archive-date=